{
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "decimals": 1,
          "max": 100,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 15 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "100 * sum(rate(shop_http_requests_total{namespace=\"demo-apps\",status=\"500\"}[5m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(shop_http_requests_total{namespace=\"demo-apps\"}[5m])), 0.001)",
          "legendFormat": "5xx %",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "HTTP 5xx error rate (cluster)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false },
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "line+area" }
          },
          "decimals": 1,
          "max": 100,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "transparent", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 15 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 16, "x": 8, "y": 0 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "100 * sum by (version) (rate(shop_http_requests_total{namespace=\"demo-apps\",status=\"500\"}[5m])) / clamp_min(sum by (version) (rate(shop_http_requests_total{namespace=\"demo-apps\"}[5m])), 0.001)",
          "legendFormat": "{{version}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "5xx error rate by version (key panel)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "decimals": 1,
          "max": 100,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 15 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "100 * sum(rate(shop_http_requests_total{namespace=\"demo-apps\",version=\"v2\",status=\"500\"}[2m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(shop_http_requests_total{namespace=\"demo-apps\",version=\"v2\"}[2m])), 0.001)",
          "legendFormat": "v2 5xx %",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Canary v2 5xx % (alert threshold 15%)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false },
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": ".*500.*" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": ".*200.*" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 16, "x": 8, "y": 6 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": [], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (version, status) (rate(shop_http_requests_total{namespace=\"demo-apps\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{version}} / {{status}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Request rate (by version & status)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false } },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 14 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "values": ["value"] },
        "pieType": "donut",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (version, status) (increase(shop_http_requests_total{namespace=\"demo-apps\"}[15m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{version}} {{status}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Requests (15m increase)",
      "type": "piechart"
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 14 },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showMiniMap": false, "showLineNumbers": false },
        "content": "### Autonomous demo cues (no UI)\n1. **Steady state** — cluster 5xx ~0%; v2 line flat.\n2. **Inject** — `failure-injection-patch.yaml` → generate traffic → **v2** line spikes (~25% of cluster 5xx at 90/10 split).\n3. **Detect** — `ShopApiCanaryHigh5xx` alert; prom-watcher invokes `local-sre`.\n4. **Recover** — after HTTPRoute shift to v1 100% → v2 500 req/s drops; cluster 5xx falls within 1–2 scrape intervals (~30s).\n\n**Say:** \"Prometheus saw it; the agent acted on SOPs; traffic moved — no human in the loop.\"",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Demo script",
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "5s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": ["shop-api", "kagent", "autonomous-sre", "demo-apps"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": { "selected": false, "text": "Prometheus", "value": "Prometheus" },
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "label": "Datasource",
        "multi": false,
        "name": "datasource",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "type": "datasource"
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": { "from": "now-30m", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "Autonomous SRE — shop-api",
  "uid": "doks-shop-api-sre",
  "version": 1,
  "weekStart": ""
}
